

=Bio=

"I am a founder of Praxis Labs Coop (http://praxis.coop) and a worker at Koumbit Networks (http://www.koumbit.org/en). Both are technology collectives committed to non-hierarchical organizational structures, transparency, free software and solidarity.

I am a core maintainer of the Aegir Hosting System (http://aegirproject.org) and developer of a number of free software projects. I have presented a number of times at local, regional and international technology conferences."


